    "summary": {
      "value": "Choose two options when using Warning Shot."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered the <strong>Sharpshooter</strong> Class, and must have acquired the <strong>Warning Shot</strong> Skill.</p><hr /><p>When you hit one or more creatures with a <strong>ranged</strong> attack and choose to deal no damage in order to gain the benefits of the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.Ovmw7cMrN6qvagG4]{Warning Shot} Skill, you may choose <strong>two</strong> options instead of one (for instance, you could inflict both <strong>shaken</strong> and <strong>slow</strong> on each creature, or inflict a status effect on each creature while also lowering their Mind Points).</p>",
